data.description: Open and bright 3 bed, 2.5 bath 2 story home in South Austin. This home has herringbone tiled floor throughout main level and bathrooms. Spacious living area open to dining area and kitchen. The kitchen features a quartz peninsula with matching quartz backsplash. Stainless gas range, microwave and dishwasher. Large master suite and Mbath w/freestanding tub and separate frameless glass shower with tile from floor to ceiling and overhead rainfall shower head. Heated floor walkway from bathroom to walk-in closet and led mirror with defogger. Lrg. utility rm and pantry. 2 car garage w/opener. Loft upstairs Fenced back yard w/storage shed and fruit trees. Cov. patio w/ext. Agent owner.
